  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to become a shadow walker? This is a top down shooter game where you fight monsters through days and nights, trying to make it to the Shadow Biome...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shadow Walker: A top down shooter with a few interesting twists. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Day Night Cycle</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874970/extras/64cb28915d83f6a05ad8ffd49fe1a612.poster.avif?t=1738366675\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874970/extras/64cb28915d83f6a05ad8ffd49fe1a612.webm?t=1738366675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874970/extras/64cb28915d83f6a05ad8ffd49fe1a612.mp4?t=1738366675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During the day, you can collect the weapons you've bought from chests, explore around, and kill a few badies here or there. During the night, be prepared to kill or be killed, hopefully gaining dozens or even hundreds of souls, which is the currency of this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Procedurally Generated Destructible Tiles</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This allows every playthrough to be a bit different. It always spawns a 4x4 grid of rooms to allow you to get a groove, and (spoiler alert) every exit is somewhere in a bottom room. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874970/extras/54c93267ca73b5b2c62ca00fbc485945.poster.avif?t=1738366675\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874970/extras/54c93267ca73b5b2c62ca00fbc485945.webm?t=1738366675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874970/extras/54c93267ca73b5b2c62ca00fbc485945.mp4?t=1738366675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TLDR: Shoot using mouse, move using wasd, buy weapons using the skulls you get from killing zombies, blow up the zombies using various weapons.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to become a shadow walker? This is a top down shooter game where you fight monsters through days and nights, trying to make it to the Shadow Biome...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shadow Walker: A top down shooter with a few interesting twists. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Day Night Cycle</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874970/extras/64cb28915d83f6a05ad8ffd49fe1a612.poster.avif?t=1738366675\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874970/extras/64cb28915d83f6a05ad8ffd49fe1a612.webm?t=1738366675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874970/extras/64cb28915d83f6a05ad8ffd49fe1a612.mp4?t=1738366675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During the day, you can collect the weapons you've bought from chests, explore around, and kill a few badies here or there. During the night, be prepared to kill or be killed, hopefully gaining dozens or even hundreds of souls, which is the currency of this world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Procedurally Generated Destructible Tiles</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This allows every playthrough to be a bit different. It always spawns a 4x4 grid of rooms to allow you to get a groove, and (spoiler alert) every exit is somewhere in a bottom room. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874970/extras/54c93267ca73b5b2c62ca00fbc485945.poster.avif?t=1738366675\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874970/extras/54c93267ca73b5b2c62ca00fbc485945.webm?t=1738366675\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874970/extras/54c93267ca73b5b2c62ca00fbc485945.mp4?t=1738366675\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TLDR: Shoot using mouse, move using wasd, buy weapons using the skulls you get from killing zombies, blow up the zombies using various weapons.</p>",
